mg src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f7133bd3b5c4160785c705b0cab66f2e318cfeb","tid":977314,"uid":15945,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ff92644ca7d69e1bceedf0c69d0982d09811aed5","tid":977314,"uid":123264,"like":843,"dislike":7,"score":836,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T05:57:03.000Z","msg":"証明樣衰仲慘過傷殘<br />\n傷殘人士都仲有人可憐比你屌<br />\n樣衰無人可憐個個都厭惡你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T08:14:23.000Z","msg":"樣衰都係殘障既一種<br />\n「樣殘」"},{"pid":"79422e7a2bdd53b1e4ce72943666b01ddd6c42d0","tid":977314,"uid":53374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T08:14:48.000Z","msg":"nick冇手冇腳都有老婆啦"},{"pid":"98960b04236ea29e169ef5060cff6da42450904c","tid":977314,"uid":171058,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"154f0b11b2c6276acf8e1822348ccf74a8f5ab67","tid":977314,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T05:53:11.000Z","msg":"美國一名25歲女子雅沃德(Hannah Aylward)，是肢體再正常不過的「正妹」，但她戀上26歲重度殘障的男子波考(Shane Burcaw)，即便兩人的感情被惡意人士大罵是「噁心、不正常」，雅沃德和波考依舊相信真愛，雅沃德還要為男生懷孕生子。<br />\n據英國《太陽報》報導，波考罹患脊髓性肌肉萎縮症(spinal muscular atrophy，簡稱SMA)，他自2歲起就過上輪椅生活。先前曾有製作公司為波考的生活拍攝紀錄片，雅沃德看過波考的紀錄片之後，和波考有了進一步接觸，兩人也越走越近成為男女朋友。<br />\n雅沃德和波考從6個月前開始，常常在網路上分享兩人的甜蜜生活，但常常遭人惡意辱罵是「噁心關係」、「不正常」。雅沃德和波考承認，要突破大眾對殘障人士的愛情刻板印象，的確很困難，但為什麼殘障人士就不能擁有正常的春天？兩人的愛情故事也曾鼓舞同樣是SMA患者的網友，為他們加油打氣。<br />\n波考說，他和雅沃德現在的任務，就是要鼓勵更多的殘障人士，能夠擁有正常的愛情，就像他們一樣。波考也說，讓他最難過的是，雅沃德和他一起出門，多數旁人都會投射異樣眼光，「有人以為我們兩人是兄弟姊妹，或者以為雅沃德是看護，還有人以為她是我媽」。兩人雖然還有很多困難要挑戰，但兩人堅信忠貞的愛情不會改變。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190111/640_253d34a869588a9d5d2c389ba5ba67ba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190111%2F640_253d34a869588a9d5d2c389ba5ba67ba.jpg&h=bf9f8eae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190111/640_b5a9cd2f31e921f8941bf2a5a6eb7950.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190111%2F640_b5a9cd2f31e921f8941bf2a5a6eb7950.jpg&h=f13ff15e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190111/640_6dbecd25549c01ee4e0a9557196d9b99.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190111%2F640_6dbecd25549c01ee4e0a9557196d9b99.jpg&h=ea39cef9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190111/640_a150557864f24fb250ce5a3148b6aa93.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190111%2F640_a150557864f24fb250ce5a3148b6aa93.jpg&h=fdc16d79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190111/640_7720c998718541a18516d15aefcd3140.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190111%2F640_7720c998718541a18516d15aefcd3140.jpg&h=63ecfec5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190111/1498776/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190111%2F1498776%2F&d=9wyTkkYHe0N7GaLerPJJfP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=d945f95b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190111%2F1498776%2F&h=11dfcfbb\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190111/1498776/</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T08:19:52.000Z","msg":"其實佢地自己唔周圍揚，邊個得閒理佢地"},{"pid":"98b40a66a9244a769282a256da20ec0ceb5c445a","tid":977314,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T08:20:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cc19a6d8b59442a8bf586486a3fd51c3053950